@Marsha34 @Aquinas18 My impression of a crowded TJ Maxx in Arkansas...

I see that COVID-19 will be 'winning' the race with the dumbed-down ppl of Arkansas, who pathetically chose to go to TJ Maxx when they were finally freed of the alleged repression they felt from being cooped up w/their families.
